metadata.name: TOSHIES #1
metadata.description: Step into the pixelated world of Toshies, a new set of NFTs created by the legendary artist Chuckchee. Chuckchee is the artist behind the popular NFT collection Alpacadabraz, and has over 15 years of experience in the pixel art industry. With a talent for creating unique and imaginative works, Chuckchee is a true master of pixelart.
